<p class="text-muted leading-relaxed mb-3">|------|--------|</p>
<p class="text-muted leading-relaxed mb-3">| `9547` | RPC — ข้อมูล sync |</p>
<p class="text-muted leading-relaxed mb-3">| `9227` | P2P — gossip network |</p>

<p class="text-muted leading-relaxed mb-3">โหมด: <strong>Sequencer</strong> (เป็นคนสร้าง Block) | Engine Kind: `geth`</p>

